Function# vmnet_network_configuration_set_external_interface(_:_:)

Mac Catalyst 13.0+macOS 26.0+

```
func vmnet_network_configuration_set_external_interface(
    _ config: vmnet_network_configuration_ref,
    _ interface_name: UnsafePointer<CChar>
) -> vmnet_return_t
```

## [ Parameters ](/documentation/vmnet/vmnet_network_configuration_set_external_interface(_:_:)#parameters)

`config`The network configuration object to be modified.

`interface_name`The name of the external interface

## [Return Value](/documentation/vmnet/vmnet_network_configuration_set_external_interface(_:_:)#return-value)

VMNET_SUCCESS on success, error otherwise.

## [Discussion](/documentation/vmnet/vmnet_network_configuration_set_external_interface(_:_:)#discussion)

Configures the external interface of a vmnet network.

This is only applicable to networks of `VMNET_SHARED_MODE`.
